Mix @minced pork{250%g} with @minced beef{250%g}. Add @egg{1}, @salt, @pepper, @paprika and @bread crumbs{50%g}.
Gently knead it until firm consistency. 
Form 20 meatballs of 60 g each.

Fry on low-medium high lightly oiled pan until golden brown.

**Tip**: Use lid on pan to prevent early browning and ensure they are cooked trough.

### Sides

Serve with mashed potatoes, Swedish cucumber salad and a spoon of Lingonberry marmalade.